{
  "stem": "2004.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, the Polish Gentiles that were in the Polish part of Pustkow camp were people who were guilty of some infractions.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know how serious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But there were black marketeers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were, maybe, thieves, maybe even people that were caught in the Polish resistance.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But minor people from the Polish resistance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were put into that camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now, we were not, of course, permitted to receive any food packages.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But the Polish Gentiles were permitted to receive [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] food packages from outside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I do remember, one Christmas, the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Poldi-- which was our-- the feared Poldi which was really not-- the feared Poldi, which was really a very nice man.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Although his reputation was not, but he really was a nice man-- somehow got through to the Germans, to the German SS, that they should really take all these packages that came in, and give some of these packages to the Jews, being that it was Christmas-- in the spirit of Christmas.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he prevailed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was really a German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He didn't look like a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I mean, he was known as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they knew he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But he was really so outspoken and-- that he somehow convinced the SS to do it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So one Christmas, we got a gift.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We had food , which was not ours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But we got part of that food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And boy, what a celebration that was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, now-- coming back to--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, God-- you name it-- ham, bread, cake.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Things that we didn't see for three years, or thereabouts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was really great.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
